  <brief_title>Vitamin D Supplementation of Lactating Mothers</brief_title>
  <acronym>MAVID</acronym>
  <official_title>Effect of Vitamin D Supplementation During Lactation on Vitamin D Status, Bone Mineralisation and Body Composition of Mother and Their Exclusively Breastfed Infants.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
